Hon o yomu no ga suki desu ka;Do you like reading books?
Hobī wa arimasu ka;Do you have a hobby?
Bideogēmu o shimasu ka;Do you play video games?
Gitā o hikemasu ka;Can you play the guitar?
Ichiban suki na katsudō wa nan desu ka;What's your favorite activity?
Dansu o shimasu ka;Do you dance?
Shashin o toru no ga suki desu ka;Do you like taking photos?
Uta o utaimasu ka;Do you sing?
Chesu wa suki desu ka;Are you into chess?
Nani ka o korekushon shite imasu ka;Do you collect anything?
Niwa no sewa o shite imasu ka;Do you do gardening?
